7306	130	8054	Jo-jo74 from Philadelphia, Pa	2012-06-30 00:00:00	YEA	0	0	Oregano is a good option for sore throats. However, it's important to dilute it with something other than water, like honey or coconut oil. This way, there is less chance of throat irritation. (Oregano oil is strong! ) Option #2- Tamari soy sauce worked well as a gargle as an alternative to ACV or pickle juice.
